{"id": "1522311802283753633", "channel_id": "1522311802283753633", "author_id": "366301276071395348", "author_name": "ipowerilya", "content": "Both players had 1 character alive. Pontol exalted at liz and liz killed both Pontos and herself but won player with Pontos\nФазовая дуэль–Режим предварительной сборки——повтор боя\n\nalad（101349486）\nРёв крови и песка、Лиз、\"24\"、Мёрфи、Санга\nЖестокое приветствие、Мы непременно встретимся снова、Дрейфуя в море желаний、Рождение втайне、Забытая рука\n---------------VS--------------------\nHelleios（101182528）\nВоссоединение желаний、Даффодил、Долл、Понтос、Рамона\nЖестокое приветствие、Поэтичные минувшие дни、Ворота Истины、Момент фортуны、Шёпот\n\n253343f7-8143-353e-b73f-3c42b761b49a#P#nSPqE", "timestamp": "2026-07-02T18:43:36.850000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522311802283753633"}
{"id": "1522286581111717888", "channel_id": "1522286581111717888", "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "content": "Hameln is a limited support that has card cost\\arithmetica manipulation and double play as his main gimmick, but in recent times his effectiveness in astral reign has been a bit lacking for most teams.\n\n**His current problems are:**\n- He is supposed to be a Keyflare unit, but he normally don't generate almost any (if you haven't his personal SSR invested) because the Rondo is played for free to get the insight in the deck (that doesn't generate it), and the Overture is either removed or keep in hand until is low or 0 cost.\n- His Rouse is too slow for the price you have to pay in keyflare and arithmetica. You start to get his 0 cost cards only the turn AFTER you play it, so you will be +1 arithetica positive only 2 turn after, or have to pay even more for the card double play option. The game has become more keyflare demanding and faster for most teams, so his slower effect is difficult to make effective use of.\n\n**Proposed changes:**\n- Give his 3 cost Overture the additional effect: Generate 0.5 of the user keyflare on hit (as an example of the possible numbers). So that you are encouraged to keep the card and actually have a use for it and the extra hits it can do if it reach 0 or is double played (Similar to his SSR but minor and more versatile).\n- Make so his Rouse immediately give a 0 cost card after it has been played. So you can start to be arithmetica positive from the turn after and enable more plays.\n\nIf you have other suggestions or opinions, free to leave them in the comments to potentially update the post.", "timestamp": "2026-07-02T17:03:23.654000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522286581111717888", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-02T17:07:33.176000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Celeste_agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1522286581287747707", "filename": "Emoji_HML_O_06.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 53988, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522286581111717888/1522286581287747707/Emoji_HML_O_06.png?ex=6a47eb5b&is=6a4699db&hm=5f585caf82832805c42f2618ec8d78dd5cec6a302814c291c156835f2afd5e41&"}]}
